{"tid":491634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"字型問題","createTime":"2017-12-06T16:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T21:07:25.000Z","uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa037d8f78aae9b6ff6acc0a298440f932c572ba","tid":491634,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"有冇IT 巴打可以幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n下面係終審法院的網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/home/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fhome%2Findex.html&d=4bvcAMgvGezbI97IR41X%2BdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e8b298b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/home/index.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n我用CHROME，巳經將字型重新設定左，所有中文網站的字都係粗體，唯獨某幾個香港的網站轉唔到，如上。<br />\n<br />\n呢種字型唔知係介定為邊種語言，唔係Han，亦唔係traditonal/ simplified Han<br />\n<br />\nD幼體字真係好難讀，睇到眼盲。請求幫手"},{"pid":"8aa60d4fa7bc6ec76fa4dbffc69cf9e4443fab58","tid":491634,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T18:03:47.000Z","msg":"裝extension得唔得? 當去到某指定網站(終審法院), 就運行特別CSS(外觀)設定: <br />\n<br />\n* { font-weight:bold !important; }<br />\n<br />\n任何網頁元件(*)字體度為粗體, 而且呢個設定係優先(!important)<br />\n<br />\ncustom CSS extension, 搵到一個:<br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/user-css/okpjlejfhacmgjkmknjhadmkdbcldfcb?hl=en-US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fuser-css%2Fokpjlejfhacmgjkmknjhadmkdbcldfcb%3Fhl%3Den-US&d=4bvcAMgvGezbI97IR41X%2BdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8adc7ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/user-css/okpjlejfhacmgjkmknjhadmkdbcldfcb?hl=en-US</a><br />\n<br />\n以上為理論, 因為我冇需要咁做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418828476fe6e29dec3a1e739eab273beabd0d45","tid":491634,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T21:07:25.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打，WORK左"}]}